  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, if one of the children was sick and needed to be separated from the others, so they wouldn't all catch it, they slept in the salon because it had like a sofa bed in there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we had a huge kitchen, which was kitchen, and dining room, and entertainment center, and all that sort of stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the center of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This huge kitchen actually set in the center of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then beyond the kitchen was the children's room on the other side of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, there were two bedrooms in the front of the house, the kitchen in the middle, and then another bedroom, and then a summer kitchen, which was a little open-- well, not open, but a kitchen that would be very cool in the summertime where my mother cooked-- and a huge porch that ran the whole length of the house, inside, you know.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because to the front, we just had the three large windows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the two bedrooms faced the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But as you walked into the courtyard, the house was very long, even though, you know, it looks small from the street.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that entire length had a porch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then on the right-hand side was my mother's flowers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She had a flower garden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then there was an area where we would have a sukkah on the sukkahs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And also-- AS (ON ANSWERING MACHINE): Hello.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is Aranka.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We can't speak to you just now.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
